INSERT INTO `keke_content` VALUES ('60', '关于Javascript中的三角函数中-正切和反正切', '话说写这篇文章还是有点小压力的。嘿嘿。。。。<br />\n&nbsp;\n<div class=\"tzui-img\"><img src=\"http://keke.tanzhouedu.com/resource/content/2015/08/24/201508241558343.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其实本人的数学也不是那么好！所以昨天我在网上买了一本初中数学的三角函数的书籍，学学初中数学。。。。<br />\n正切是一个重要的三角函数，在Javascript中通过Math.tan(角度)函数来表示,它表现是对边和邻边的关系,也就是上图的<br />\nMath.tan(30 &nbsp;/<span style=\"line-height: 22.3999996185303px;\">180</span>&nbsp;*Math.PI) = B&nbsp;/ A; 等于0.577350.... 这个函数在实际开发中用的比较的少，但是它的一个对立面函数反正切 反而用的很多<br />\n<br />\n注意了其实上面的计算都是逆时针计算所以结构是一个负数，大家一定要内心里面一定要清楚这一点，<br />\nvar pv =&nbsp;<span style=\"line-height: 22.3999996185303px;\">Math.atan(0.577) * 180 / Math.PI;约等于30,那么它的实际用处到底是什么呢。他里面还有一个很重要的角色就是<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"color:#FF0000;\">红色警告:<br />\n<br />\nMath.atan2(y,x) 这个的结果返回的是一个:-3.14(-&pi;) - 3.14(&pi;)的值。<br />\n这两个参数分别代表的是:邻边和对边的比例</span></span></strong></span></div>\n<span style=\"line-height: 22.3999996185303px;\">假如上面的 y就是上面图形的B，x就是上面图形的A &nbsp;。假如A = 1.732 &nbsp;,B = 1<br />\n你可以得出一个答案是：</span><br />\nMath.atan2(1,1.732) * 180/ &nbsp;Math.PI 答案也是：30&deg;<br />\n<span style=\"line-height: 22.3999996185303px;\">Math.atan2(-1,-1.732) * 180/ &nbsp;Math.PI 答案也是：150&deg;</span><br />\n哎呀呀你会发现问题就来，两个是这么的有默契如果全部为负数的话那么他们两个加起来就是:180&deg; 也就是一个 &pi;<br />\n亲别告诉我你还是不懂，我知道你真的还不懂 &nbsp;<span style=\"line-height: 22.3999996185303px;\">Math.atan2(1,1.732)&nbsp;</span>&nbsp;~&nbsp;<span style=\"line-height: 22.3999996185303px;\">Math.atan2(-1,-1.732) 这个才是，因为我把它换算成了角度。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color:#FF0000;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">案例分析:</span></strong></span></span><br />\n那这个函数到底有吗作用呢，假如我们有一个\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n盒子的宽度和高度都是200 ，接下来我要判断我的鼠标是从进入盒子的什么判断是从哪个方向进入，<br />\n说清楚点就是：盒子的四个方向：上，右，下，左，我们开始冥想肯定要有：<br />\na ： 一个状态码 分别代表 0 1 2 3 那该多好，这个是目标<br />\nb &nbsp;: &nbsp;Math.atan2和这个有什么关系呢<br />\nc ：开始注意观察我们如果判断水平方向的时候把盒子一分二，从鼠标的左边移入的时候（e.pageX || e.clientX） - 盒子左边的一半 这个时候可能会得到,<br />\n代码如下：\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"line-height:20px; font-size:14px;font-family:Consolas,Courier New,Inconsolata-g,DejaVu Sans Mono,微软雅黑,宋体;color:#f9f9f9;\" width=\"100%\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr style=\"background-color:#1b2426;\" valign=\"top\">\n			<td style=\"border:0px; border-right-color:#435a5f; border-right-width:3px; color:#b9bdb6; border-right-style:solid; text-align:right; padding-right:5px; width:40px;\">1</td>\n			<td style=\"border:0px; padding-left:10px; text-align:left;\">\n			<div id=\"box\">&nbsp;</div>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr style=\"background-color:#323232;\" valign=\"top\">\n			<td style=\"border:0px; border-right-color:#435a5f; border-right-width:3px; color:#b9bdb6; border-right-style:solid; text-align:right; padding-right:5px; width:40px;\">2</td>\n			<td style=\"border:0px; padding-left:10px; text-align:left;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"color:#5ba1cf\"><script type=\"text/javascript\"></span></td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr style=\"background-color:#1b2426;\" valign=\"top\">\n			<td style=\"border:0px; border-right-color:#435a5f; border-right-width:3px; color:#b9bdb6; border-right-style:solid; text-align:right; padding-right:5px; width:40px;\">3</td>\n			<td style=\"border:0px; padding-left:10px; text-align:left;\">  window.onload = function(){</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr style=\"background-color:#323232;\" valign=\"top\">\n			<td style=\"border:0px; border-right-color:#435a5f; border-right-width:3px; color:#b9bdb6; border-right-style:solid; text-align:right; padding-right:5px; width:40px;\">4</td>\n			<td style=\"border:0px; padding-left:10px; text-align:left;\">   document.getElementById(\"box\").onmouseenter = function(e){</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr style=\"background-color:#1b2426;\" valign=\"top\">\n			<td style=\"border:0px; border-right-color:#435a5f; border-right-width:3px; color:#b9bdb6; border-right-style:solid; text-align:right; padding-right:5px; width:40px;\">5</td>\n			<td style=\"border:0px; padding-left:10px; text-align:left;\">     var w = this.offsetWidth;</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr style=\"background-color:#323232;\" valign=\"top\">\n			<td style=\"border:0px; border-right-color:#435a5f; border-right-width:3px; color:#b9bdb6; border-right-style:solid; text-align:right; padding-right:5px; width:40px;\">6</td>\n			<td style=\"border:0px; padding-left:10px; text-align:left;\">     var h = this.offsetHeight;</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr style=\"background-color:#1b2426;\" valign=\"top\">\n			<td style=\"border:0px; border-right-color:#435a5f; border-right-width:3px; color:#b9bdb6; border-right-style:solid; text-align:right; padding-right:5px; width:40px;\">7</td>\n			<td style=\"border:0px; padding-left:10px; text-align:left;\">     var x = (e.clientX - this.offsetLeft - (w / 2)) * (w > h ? (h / w) : 1);</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr style=\"background-color:#323232;\" valign=\"top\">\n			<td style=\"border:0px; border-right-color:#435a5f; border-right-width:3px; color:#b9bdb6; border-right-style:solid; text-align:right; padding-right:5px; width:40px;\">8</td>\n			<td style=\"border:0px; padding-left:10px; text-align:left;\">     var y = (e.clientY - this.offsetTop - (h / 2)) * (h > w ? (w / h) : 1);</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr style=\"background-color:#1b2426;\" valign=\"top\">\n			<td style=\"border:0px; border-right-color:#435a5f; border-right-width:3px; color:#b9bdb6; border-right-style:solid; text-align:right; padding-right:5px; width:40px;\">9</td>\n			<td style=\"border:0px; padding-left:10px; text-align:left;\">     var direction = Math.round(((Math.atan2(y, x) * (180 / Math.PI)<span style=\"color: rgb(249, 249, 249); font-family: Consolas, \'Courier New\', Inconsolata-g, \'DejaVu Sans Mono\', 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 20px; background-color: rgb(27, 36, 38);\"> + 180</span>)) / 90) ;</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr style=\"background-color:#323232;\" valign=\"top\">\n			<td style=\"border:0px; border-right-color:#435a5f; border-right-width:3px; color:#b9bdb6; border-right-style:solid; text-align:right; padding-right:5px; width:40px;\">10</td>\n			<td style=\"border:0px; padding-left:10px; text-align:left;\">    console.log((direction + 3) % 4);</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr style=\"background-color:#1b2426;\" valign=\"top\">\n			<td style=\"border:0px; border-right-color:#435a5f; border-right-width:3px; color:#b9bdb6; border-right-style:solid; text-align:right; padding-right:5px; width:40px;\">11</td>\n			<td style=\"border:0px; padding-left:10px; text-align:left;\">   };</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr style=\"background-color:#323232;\" valign=\"top\">\n			<td style=\"border:0px; border-right-color:#435a5f; border-right-width:3px; color:#b9bdb6; border-right-style:solid; text-align:right; padding-right:5px; width:40px;\">12</td>\n			<td style=\"border:0px; padding-left:10px; text-align:left;\">  }</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr style=\"background-color:#1b2426;\" valign=\"top\">\n			<td style=\"border:0px; border-right-color:#435a5f; border-right-width:3px; color:#b9bdb6; border-right-style:solid; text-align:right; padding-right:5px; width:40px;\">13</td>\n			<td style=\"border:0px; padding-left:10px; text-align:left;\"> <span style=\"color:#5ba1cf\"></script></span></td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n<br />\n上是：2 &nbsp; 右是：3 下是 ：0 &nbsp;左是:1 &nbsp; 如果给元素加+180&deg;就会翻转<br />\n上右下左：0 ,1 ,2 ,3<br />\n<br />\n整体的案例如下：<br />\n<a href=\"http://keke.tanzhouedu.com/code/60\">点击查看源代码</a><br />\n<title></title>\n<br />\n完结。。。。 哪里写的不正确留言指出。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"line-height: 22.3999996185303px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<style type=\"text/css\"></span></td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr style=\"background-color:#1b2426;\" valign=\"top\">\n			<td style=\"border:0px; border-right-color:#435a5f; border-right-width:3px; color:#b9bdb6; border-right-style:solid; text-align:right; padding-right:5px; width:40px;\">11</td>\n			<td style=\"border:0px; padding-left:10px; text-align:left;\"> *{padding:0;margin:0}</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr style=\"background-color:#323232;\" valign=\"top\">\n			<td style=\"border:0px; border-right-color:#435a5f; border-right-width:3px; color:#b9bdb6; border-right-style:solid; text-align:right; padding-right:5px; width:40px;\">12</td>\n			<td style=\"border:0px; padding-left:10px; text-align:left;\"> </td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr style=\"background-color:#1b2426;\" valign=\"top\">\n			<td style=\"border:0px; border-right-color:#435a5f; border-right-width:3px; color:#b9bdb6; border-right-style:solid; text-align:right; padding-right:5px; width:40px;\">13</td>\n			<td style=\"border:0px; padding-left:10px; text-align:left;\"> #box{width:200px;height:200px;background:red;margin:100px;position:relative;}</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr style=\"background-color:#323232;\" valign=\"top\">\n			<td style=\"border:0px; border-right-color:#435a5f; border-right-width:3px; color:#b9bdb6; border-right-style:solid; text-align:right; padding-right:5px; width:40px;\">14</td>\n			<td style=\"border:0px; padding-left:10px; text-align:left;\"> #box .info{position:absolute;background:rgba(0,0,0,0.7);text-align:center;line-height:200px;font-size:56px;color:#fff}</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr style=\"background-color:#1b2426;\" valign=\"top\">\n			<td style=\"border:0px; border-right-color:#435a5f; border-right-width:3px; color:#b9bdb6; border-right-style:solid; text-align:right; padding-right:5px; width:40px;\">15</td>\n			<td style=\"border:0px; padding-left:10px; text-align:left;\">  <span style=\"color:#5ba1cf\">\n</style>\n', '2015-08-24 15:57:12', '2015-08-31 17:10:23', '1', '反正切，三角函数', '1', '0', '1', '8', 'resource/content/2015/08/24/201508241556020.gif', '1', '1', null, '71', '0', '0', 'pages/js/2015/08/24/60Fedwc2Pv.html', '反正切，三角函数', 'Math.atan2(y,x) 这个的结果返回的是一个:-3.14(-π) - 3.14(π)的值。这两个参数分别代表的是:邻边和对边的比例', null, '3', null, '1', 'window.onload = function(){\r\n	document.getElementById(\"box\").onmouseenter = function(e){\r\n		var w = this.offsetWidth;\r\n		var h = this.offsetHeight;\r\n		var x = (e.clientX - this.offsetLeft - (w / 2)) * (w > h ? (h / w) : 1);\r\n		var y = (e.clientY - this.offsetTop - (h / 2)) * (h > w ? (w / h) : 1);\r\n		var direction = Math.round(((Math.atan2(y, x) * (180 / Math.PI) + 180)) / 90) ;\r\n		var num = (direction + 3) % 4;\r\n		var cdom = this.children[0];\r\n\r\n		if(num == 0){\r\n			cdom.style.top = 0+\"px\";\r\n			cdom.style.width = \"100%\";\r\n			$(cdom).animate({height:200})\r\n			cdom.innerHTML= \"上\";\r\n		}else if(num ==1){\r\n			cdom.style.right = 0+\"px\";\r\n			cdom.style.height = \"100%\";\r\n			$(cdom).animate({width:200});\r\n			cdom.innerHTML= \"右\";\r\n		}else if(num ==2){\r\n			cdom.style.bottom = 0+\"px\";\r\n			cdom.style.width = \"100%\";\r\n			$(cdom).animate({height:200});\r\n			cdom.innerHTML= \"下\";\r\n		}else if(num ==3){\r\n			cdom.style.left = 0+\"px\";\r\n			cdom.style.height = \"100%\";\r\n				$(cdom).animate({width:200})\r\n			cdom.innerHTML= \"左\";\r\n		}\r\n	};\r\n\r\n	document.getElementById(\"box\").onmouseleave = function(){\r\n		var cdom = this.children[0];\r\n		cdom.innerHTML =\"\";\r\n		cdom.removeAttribute(\"style\");\r\n	}\r\n}\r\n\r\n', '<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"http://keke.tanzhouedu.com/sg/jquery-1.11.2.min.js\"></script>\r\n\r\n<h1 style=\"padding:20px;\">鼠标移动到红色框框内试试看！！！！</h1>\r\n<div id=\"box\">\r\n  <div class=\"info\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n', '*{padding:0;margin:0}\r\n#box{width:200px;height:200px;background:red;margin:100px;position:relative;}\r\n#box .info{position:absolute;background:rgba(0,0,0,0.7);text-align:center;line-height:200px;font-size:56px;color:#fff}\r\n\r\n', null, null, null);
INSERT INTO `keke_content` VALUES ('61', '模拟类似Tumblr弹出式菜单Menu特效', '<span style=\"color:#F0FFFF;\"><span style=\"line-height: 22.3999996185303px;\">今天早上8.00起来写这玩意，这些玩意一直羁绊着我的技术生涯，搞定你不休息。。。。。</span><br />\n最近很多想法，看见很多国外的网站很多很酷很炫的用户提样的效果，模拟了一个国外轻博客网站的弹出式菜单效果。<br />\n做这个也可以使用css3的动画函数实现，不小心我刚才没备份给删掉了。。。。<br />\n后面我在补上。。。。</span><br />\n&nbsp;', '2015-08-25 10:38:55', '2015-08-25 11:35:19', '1', '菜单,menu', '1', '0', '1', '8', 'resource/content/2015/08/25/201508251037420.gif', '1', '1', null, '58', '0', '0', 'pages/js/2015/08/25/61ijwWGKba.html', '菜单,menu', '最近很多想法，看见很多国外的网站很多很酷很炫的用户提样的效果，模拟了一个国外轻博客网站的弹出式菜单效果。\r\n', null, '3', null, '1', 'window.onload = function(){\n		document.getElementById(\"overlay\").onclick = function(){\n			var index = 3;\n			var start = 3;\n			var timer = setInterval(function(){\n				if(start<=0 && index==7){\n					document.getElementById(\"glassbox\").style.display = \"none\";\n					clearInterval(timer);\n				}else{\n					move(document.getElementsByClassName(\"item\")[index],{top:-1000});\n					move(document.getElementsByClassName(\"item\")[start],{top:-1000});\n					index++;\n					start--;\n				}\n			},100);\n		};\n\n		expand();\n		\n	};\n\n	function expand(e){\n		document.getElementById(\"glassbox\").style.display = \"block\";\n		var index = 3;\n		var start = 3;\n		var timer = setInterval(function(){\n			if(start<=0 && index==7){\n				clearInterval(timer);\n			}else{\n				move(document.getElementsByClassName(\"item\")[index],{top:140});\n				move(document.getElementsByClassName(\"item\")[start],{top:140});\n				index++;\n				start--;\n			}\n		},100);\n		if(e)e.stopPropagation();\n	}\n\n	//动画函数\n	function move(obj,opts,callback){\n		clearInterval(obj.timer);//清楚多余动画	\n		//定时动画\n		obj.timer = setInterval(function(){\n			var imark = true;\n			for(var attr in opts){//永远都是false\n				attr = attr.toLowerCase();\n				//获取起点坐标\n				var start;\n				if(attr == \"opacity\"){\n					start = Math.round(getCss( obj, \'opacity\') * 100);\n				}else{\n					start = parseInt(getCss(obj,attr));\n				}\n				//速度\n				var speed = (opts[attr] - start) /8;\n				//速度精度计算，如果是正小数那么向上取值，如果负数就向下取值，为什么，因为有精度的丢失的问题\n				speed = speed > 0  ? Math.ceil(speed) : Math.floor(speed);\n				\n				if(start != opts[attr]){//到达终点 0\n					imark = false;\n					if(attr==\"opacity\"){\n						console.log(start+\"====\"+speed);\n						obj.style.opacity = (start + speed) / 100;\n						obj.style.filter = \'alpha(opacity=\'+ (start + speed) +\')\';\n					}else{\n						obj.style[attr] = start+speed+\"px\";//start + speed已经走了距离\n					}\n				}\n			};\n			\n			if(imark){\n				clearInterval(obj.timer);//之前动画是不还执行\n				if(callback)callback.call(obj);\n			}\n		},30);//没隔30毫秒执行一帧动画\n	};\n\n	//获取样式的起点左边的位置\n	function getCss(obj,attr){\n		 var val = obj.currentStyle ? obj.currentStyle[attr] : window.getComputedStyle(obj,null)[attr];\n		 return val == \"auto\" ? 0 :val;\n	};\n\n', ' <div id=\"overlay\"  class=\"post-tab-switching finish-animating\">\n  <h1 style=\"color:#111;padding:100px\">点击空白区域可以收回去 \n  </h1><a href=\"javascript:void(0);\" style=\"color:#111;padding:100px\" onclick=\"expand(event)\">点击展开</a>\n \n	  <div class=\"tab-post-types count-7\">\n		<div class=\"tab-post-type item\">\n			<div class=\"post-type-icon icon-text\" >\n				<i class=\"post-type-icon-overlay\"></i>\n			</div>\n			<div class=\"post-type-name\" >\n				<span class=\"post-type-name-span\">Text</span>\n			</div>\n		  </div>\n		  <div class=\"tab-post-type item\">\n			<div class=\"post-type-icon icon-text\" >\n				<i class=\"post-type-icon-overlay\"></i>\n			</div>\n			<div class=\"post-type-name\" >\n				<span class=\"post-type-name-span\">Text</span>\n			</div>\n		  </div>\n		  <div class=\"tab-post-type item\">\n			<div class=\"post-type-icon icon-text\" >\n				<i class=\"post-type-icon-overlay\"></i>\n			</div>\n			<div class=\"post-type-name\" >\n				<span class=\"post-type-name-span\">Text</span>\n			</div>\n		  </div>\n		  <div class=\"tab-post-type item\">\n			<div class=\"post-type-icon icon-text\" >\n				<i class=\"post-type-icon-overlay\"></i>\n			</div>\n			<div class=\"post-type-name\" >\n				<span class=\"post-type-name-span\">Text</span>\n			</div>\n		  </div>\n		  <div class=\"tab-post-type item\">\n			<div class=\"post-type-icon icon-text\" >\n				<i class=\"post-type-icon-overlay\"></i>\n			</div>\n			<div class=\"post-type-name\" >\n				<span class=\"post-type-name-span\">Text</span>\n			</div>\n		  </div>\n		  <div class=\"tab-post-type item\">\n			<div class=\"post-type-icon icon-text\" >\n				<i class=\"post-type-icon-overlay\"></i>\n			</div>\n			<div class=\"post-type-name\" >\n				<span class=\"post-type-name-span\">Text</span>\n			</div>\n		  </div>\n		  <div class=\"tab-post-type item\">\n			<div class=\"post-type-icon icon-text\" >\n				<i class=\"post-type-icon-overlay\"></i>\n			</div>\n			<div class=\"post-type-name\" >\n				<span class=\"post-type-name-span\">Text</span>\n			</div>\n		  </div>\n	  </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div id=\"glassbox\" class=\"glass blue\"></div>\n\n', '*{padding:0;margin:0}\n	a{text-decoration:none;color:#333}\n	.post-tab-switching{position:fixed;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;left:0;z-index:3;background-size:100% 100%;opacity:1}\n	.tab-post-types{position:fixed;top:30%;left:50%;margin-top:-115px}\n	.tab-post-types.count-7{margin-left:-440px;width:880px}\n	.tab-post-types .tab-post-type:nth-child(1) .post-type-icon{background-position:0 0}\n	.tab-post-types .tab-post-type:nth-child(2) .post-type-icon{background-position:0 -100px}\n	.tab-post-types .tab-post-type:nth-child(3) .post-type-icon{background-position:0 -200px}\n	.tab-post-types .tab-post-type:nth-child(4) .post-type-icon{background-position:0 -300px}\n	.tab-post-types .tab-post-type:nth-child(5) .post-type-icon{background-position:0 -400px}\n	.tab-post-types .tab-post-type:nth-child(6) .post-type-icon{background-position:0 -500px}\n	.tab-post-types .tab-post-type:nth-child(7) .post-type-icon{background-position:0 -600px}\n	.tab-post-type{position:relative;width:100px;height:100px;float:left;cursor:pointer;margin-right:30px}\n	.tab-post-type:last-child{margin-right:0}\n	.tab-post-type .post-type-icon,.tab-post-type .post-type-name{position:relative;display:block;opacity:1}\n	.tab-post-type .post-type-icon{height:100%;width:100%;z-index:2;background-image:url(\'https://secure.assets.tumblr.com/images/quick_compose_sprite.png?v=a9092a0967f882ab67dd7e721f555044\')}\n	.tab-post-type \n	\n	\n	.post-type-name{text-decoration:none;font-size:18px;color:#fff;font-weight:200;text-align:center;white-space:nowrap;text-overflow:ellipsis;margin:10px 0 0 -10px;width:100%;text-shadow:none;overflow:hidden;padding:0 10px 10px;z-index:1}\n	.tab-post-type .post-type-name .post-type-name-span{width:200px;text-align:center}\n	.post-tab-switching.finish-animating .tab-post-type:hover .post-type-icon{transition:-webkit-transform .1s linear;transition:transform .1s linear;-webkit-transform:scale(1.07)!important;-ms-transform:scale(1.07)!important;transform:scale(1.07)!important}\n	.post-tab-switching.finish-animating .tab-post-type:active .post-type-icon{transition:-webkit-transform .1s linear;transition:transform .1s linear;-webkit-transform:scale(1)!important;-ms-transform:scale(1)!important;transform:scale(1)!important}\n	.post-tab-switching.finish-animating .tab-post-type.selected .post-type-icon{transition:-webkit-transform .1s linear;transition:transform .1s linear;-webkit-transform:scale(1.07)!important;-ms-transform:scale(1.07)!important;transform:scale(1.07)!important}\n\n	\n	.glass, #hello_glass, #glass_overlay {\n	 \n	  position: fixed;\n	  top: 0;\n	  left: 0;\n	  height: 100%;\n	  width: 100%;\n	  z-index: 2147483646;\n	  background-color: transparent;\n	  opacity: 1;\n	  -webkit-touch-callout: none;\n	  -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\n	  -webkit-user-select: none;\n	  -moz-user-select: none;\n	  -ms-user-select: none;\n	  user-select: none;\n	}\n\n	.blue.glass, .blue#hello_glass, .blue#glass_overlay {\n	  transition: background-color .2s linear;\n	  background: rgba(54,70,93,.5);\n	  z-index: -1;\n	}\n\n', null, null, null);
INSERT INTO `keke_content` VALUES ('62', '我们不必克制彼此心里的激情', '我张望着望不到的天空，正如我期盼着永远期盼不到的你。人们总说时光可以解决一切，而我却只能在这时光里迷失，徘徊，寻找着那没有答案的答案。<br />\n<br />\n初三，初三似乎是一道坎。每个人似乎都变得很忙碌，忙着升学，忙着调研考，亦或是其他。那些朝夕相处的人，关系似乎更近了，而那些远在他处的人似乎联系越来越少。<br />\n<br />\n以至于有时候自己都不相信，到底，是时间改变了一切，还是距离。甚至怀疑当初的承诺是否还能等到实现的那一天？<br />\n迷茫，让我们的生活像水一样平乏无味却又无处不在，久而久之，渗透出汩汩水流，汇而成海，并且只有自己才能将自己摆渡到彼岸。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;', '2015-08-26 20:18:53', '2015-08-30 14:40:42', '1', '', '1', '0', '1', '3', 'resource/content/2015/08/26/201508262018520.jpg', '1', '1', null, '12', '0', '0', 'pages/c/2015/08/26/62g6GeInbW.html', '', '', '', '2', '3', null, null, null, null, '540', '540', '');
INSERT INTO `keke_content` VALUES ('63', 'Javascript结合动画实现波形文字', '<span style=\"color:#F0FFFF;\">结合Javascript中的正弦和余弦实现一个跳跃的文字，是不是挺可爱的。</span>', '2015-08-30 14:39:11', '2015-09-25 19:20:26', '1', '', '1', '0', '1', '8', 'resource/content/2015/08/30/201508301438263.gif', '1', '1', null, '44', '0', '0', 'pages/js/2015/08/30/63VFZxQpvP.html', '', '', null, '3', null, '1', '/*\n波纹效果\nwindow.onload = function(){\n			\n			shakeCharacter(\"box\");	\n			\n			function shakeCharacter(id){\n				var boxDom = document.getElementById(id);\n				var text = boxDom.innerText;\n				var html = \"\";\n\n				for(var i=0;i<text.length;i++){\n					html += \"<span>\"+text[i]+\"</span>\";\n				}\n				boxDom.innerHTML = html;\n				var arr = [];\n				var spanDoms = boxDom.children;\n				for(var i=0;i<spanDoms.length;i++){\n					spanDoms[i].style.left = spanDoms[i].offsetLeft+\"px\";\n					spanDoms[i].style.top = spanDoms[i].offsetTop+\"px\";\n					arr.push({left:spanDoms[i].offsetLeft,top:spanDoms[i].offsetTop})\n				}\n				for(var i=0;i<spanDoms.length;i++){\n					spanDoms[i].style.position = \"absolute\";\n				}\n				\n				var index = 0; \n				var speed = 1;\n				var timer = setInterval(function(){\n					if(index ==spanDoms.length){\n						speed =0;\n						index=0;\n						for(var i=0;i<arr.length;i++){\n							spanDoms[i].style.left = arr[i].left+\"px\";\n							spanDoms[i].style.top = arr[i].top+\"px\";\n						}\n					}else{\n						spanDoms[index].style.top = spanDoms[index].offsetTop+Math.cos(speed)*3+\"px\";\n						spanDoms[index].style.left = spanDoms[index].offsetLeft+Math.sin(speed)*3+\"px\";\n						speed +=0.5;\n						index++;\n					}\n				},30);\n			}\n		};\n\n*/\n\nwindow.onload = function(){\n			shakeCharacter(\"box\");	\n			function shakeCharacter(id){\n				var boxDom = document.getElementById(id);\n				var text = boxDom.innerText;\n				var html = \"\";\n\n				for(var i=0;i<text.length;i++){\n					html += \"<span>\"+text[i]+\"</span>\";\n				}\n				boxDom.innerHTML = html;\n				var arr = [];\n				var spanDoms = boxDom.children;\n				for(var i=0;i<spanDoms.length;i++){\n					spanDoms[i].style.left = spanDoms[i].offsetLeft+\"px\";\n					spanDoms[i].style.top = spanDoms[i].offsetTop+\"px\";\n					arr.push({left:spanDoms[i].offsetLeft,top:spanDoms[i].offsetTop})\n				}\n				for(var i=0;i<spanDoms.length;i++){\n					spanDoms[i].style.position = \"absolute\";\n					spanDoms[i].style.left = \"-100px\"\n				}\n				\n				function right(){\n					var index = 1; \n					var speed = 0;\n					var timer = setInterval(function(){\n							if(index==(arr.length+1)){\n								clearInterval(timer);\n								index = 0;\n								left();\n								//down();\n							}else{\n								speed = (arr[arr.length-index].left - spanDoms[arr.length-index].offsetLeft)*0.752; \n								speed = speed > 0  ? Math.ceil(speed) : Math.floor(speed);\n								spanDoms[arr.length-index].style.left = spanDoms[arr.length-index].offsetLeft + speed+\"px\";\n								if(speed == 0){\n									index++;\n								}\n							}\n					},30);\n				}\n\n\n				function left(){\n					var index = 0; \n					var speed = 10;\n					var timer = setInterval(function(){\n						if(index==arr.length){\n							clearInterval(timer);\n							index = 1;\n							right();\n						}else{\n							var icur = (spanDoms[index].offsetLeft - speed);\n							speed *= 1.015;\n							spanDoms[index].style.left = icur+\"px\"; \n							if(icur<=0){\n								spanDoms[index].style.left = \"-100px\"; \n								index++;\n							}\n						}\n					},30);\n				}\n\n\n				function down(){\n					var index = 0; \n					var speed = 10;\n					var timer = setInterval(function(){\n						if(index==arr.length){\n							clearInterval(timer);\n							index = 1;\n						}else{\n							var icur = spanDoms[index].offsetTop -speed;\n							speed +=1;\n							spanDoms[index].style.top = icur+\"px\"; \n							if(icur<=-1000){\n								index++;\n							}\n						}\n					},30);\n				}\n\n				right();\n			}\n		};\n\n\n\n\n', '<div id=\"box\">I Love You!!!!</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n', '*{padding:0;margin:0}\nbody{background:#1F53A0;font-size:14px;font-family:\"微软雅黑\"}\n#box{margin:100px auto;text-align:center;font-size:36px;font-weight:700;color:#fff;}\n\n\n\n\n\n\n', '540', '540', null);
INSERT INTO `keke_content` VALUES ('64', 'Javascript实现图片放大镜', '<div class=\"tzui-img\"><img src=\"http://keke.tanzhouedu.com/resource/content/2015/09/07/201509071735200.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" /></div>\n<br />\n<span style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\">学会做一个现实的放大镜，使用Javascript和CSS3的玻璃。悬停在图像上方看动作。<br />\n该代码使用CSS3 box-shadow和border-radius属性来创建放大镜。<span style=\"line-height: 22.3999996185303px;\">Javascript</span>是用来放置在光标的坐标和改变相应的背景位置。<br />\n移动光标远离图像，轻轻地淡出了放大镜将图像恢复到默认状态。</span>', '2015-09-06 15:15:00', '2015-10-10 19:36:29', '1', '放大,放大镜,图像', '1', '0', '1', '8', 'resource/content/2015/09/06/201509061512553.gif', '1', '1', null, '31', '0', '0', 'pages/js/2015/09/06/64BF95aTrX.html', '放大,放大镜,图像', '学会做一个现实的放大镜，使用Javascript和CSS3的玻璃。悬停在图像上方看动作。该代码使用CSS3 box-shadow和border-radius属性来创建放大镜。Javascript是用来放置在光标的坐标和改变相应的背景位置。移动光标远离图像，轻轻地淡出了放大镜将图像恢复到默认状态。', null, '3', null, '1', 'window.onload = function(){\n	var largeDom = document.getElementsByClassName(\"large\")[0];\n	var imgDom = document.getElementsByClassName(\"small\")[0];\n	document.getElementsByClassName(\"magnify\")[0].onmousemove = function(e){\n		var ev = e || window.event;\n		var mx = ev.clientX - this.offsetLeft;\n		var my = ev.clientY - this.offsetTop;\n		//判断放大镜是否已经和图片接触到了 \n		if(mx < this.clientWidth && my <this.clientHeight && mx>0 && my>0){\n			largeDom.style.display = \"block\";\n		}else{\n			largeDom.style.display = \"none\";\n		}\n\n		//放大镜的位置\n		var left = mx - largeDom.clientWidth/2 ;\n		var top = my -largeDom.clientHeight/2;\n\n		//图片的坐标位置的换算\n		var img  = new Image();\n		img.src =imgDom.src;\n		var iw = img.width;\n		var ih = img.height;\n		//计算出当前鼠标所在图片的位置的比例\n		var bx = (mx / imgDom.clientWidth*iw - largeDom.clientWidth/2)*-1+\"px\";\n		var by = (my / imgDom.clientHeight*ih -largeDom.clientHeight/2)*-1+\"px\";\n\n		largeDom.style.left = left +\"px\";\n		largeDom.style.top = top +\"px\";\n		largeDom.style.backgroundPosition = bx +\" \"+by;\n	};\n};\n', '<div class=\"magnify\">\n	<div class=\"large\"></div>\n	<img class=\"small\" src=\"http://thecodeplayer.com/uploads/media/iphone.jpg\" width=\"200\"/>\n</div>\n\n\n', '* {margin: 0; padding: 0;}\n.magnify {width: 200px; margin: 50px auto; position: relative;}\n.large {\n  width: 175px; height: 175px;\n  position: absolute;\n  border-radius: 100%;\n  /*Multiple box shadows to achieve the glass effect*/\n  box-shadow: 0 0 0 7px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85), \n    0 0 7px 7px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25), \n    inset 0 0 40px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);\n  /*Lets load up the large image first*/\n  background: url(\'http://thecodeplayer.com/uploads/media/iphone.jpg\') no-repeat;\n  /*hide the glass by default*/\n  display: none;\n}\n\n.small { display: block; }\n\n', '1040', '600', null);
INSERT INTO `keke_content` VALUES ('65', '漫天纷飞的银杏森林', '<span style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, 微软雅黑, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 22px;\">心中有爱时，总想把美好芳香送给对方，这样会让自己发现世界的极美。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: Verdana, 微软雅黑, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 22px;\" />\n<span style=\"font-family: Verdana, 微软雅黑, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 22px;\">心中有爱时，笔下无以复加的文字，隐藏在音乐的深处，似乎比华丽绚烂的光与影像来的更为情真意切。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: Verdana, 微软雅黑, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 22px;\" />\n<br style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: Verdana, 微软雅黑, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 22px;\" />\n<span style=\"font-family: Verdana, 微软雅黑, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 22px;\">我多怕自己会有所改变，又多怕自己永不改变。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: Verdana, 微软雅黑, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 22px;\" />\n<span style=\"font-family: Verdana, 微软雅黑, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 22px;\">因我心中一直有爱。</span></span>', '2015-09-06 16:47:00', '2015-09-07 01:02:52', '1', '', '1', '0', '1', '8', 'resource/content/2015/09/06/201509061646591.jpg', '1', '1', null, '6', '0', '0', 'pages/c/2015/09/06/65mkbFiqga.html', '', '', '', '2', '11', null, null, null, null, '500', '500', 'undefined');
INSERT INTO `keke_content` VALUES ('66', '在木星', '<span style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\">君归来 君归来<br />\n待历经沧海 待阅尽悲欢<br />\n心方倦知返<br />\n君已尘满面 污泥满身<br />\n好个白发迷途人<br />\n今日归来不晚 彩霞濯满天<br />\n明月作烛台<br />\n亦归来 亦归来<br />\n以苦难为船 以泪为帆<br />\n心似离弦箭<br />\n莫说天无涯 海无岸<br />\n纵然归程须万载<br />\n今日归来不晚 与故人重来<br />\n天真作少年。。。。</span><br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;', '2015-09-06 17:01:24', '2015-09-06 17:18:56', '1', '', '1', '0', '1', '8', 'resource/content/2015/09/06/201509061701230.jpg', '1', '1', null, '10', '0', '0', 'pages/c/2015/09/06/66YZJ8evbU.html', '', '', '', '2', '3', null, null, null, null, '540', '540', 'undefined');
INSERT INTO `keke_content` VALUES ('67', '季节的问候', '<span style=\"color:#FAEBD7;\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, 微软雅黑, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 22px;\">我想看你青春的脸，但是你却给我看你垂垂老矣的容颜。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: Verdana, 微软雅黑, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 22px;\" />\n<span style=\"font-family: Verdana, 微软雅黑, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 22px;\">而这一切不应该是这样的。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: Verdana, 微软雅黑, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 22px;\" />\n<br style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: Verdana, 微软雅黑, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 22px;\" />\n<span style=\"font-family: Verdana, 微软雅黑, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 22px;\">我希望能够带给你的不止是个人情绪和青春伤逝的无限沉溺。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: Verdana, 微软雅黑, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 22px;\" />\n<span style=\"font-family: Verdana, 微软雅黑, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 22px;\">我希望能够在打开你记忆的同时能够保持平静，更愿意自由的活着。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: Verdana, 微软雅黑, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 22px;\" />\n<span style=\"font-family: Verdana, 微软雅黑, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 22px;\">我希望能够让你觉得没有什么东西比拥有灿烂的灵魂而更值得庆祝。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: Verdana, 微软雅黑, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 22px;\" />\n<span style=\"font-family: Verdana, 微软雅黑, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 22px;\">我希望能够让你在时代腐朽的风中探寻生命切实的意义，让灵魂安然释放。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: Verdana, 微软雅黑, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 22px;\" />\n<span style=\"font-family: Verdana, 微软雅黑, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 22px;\">我希望能促使你找到这个物欲城市的病灶，让你拥有清醒的声音以敲碎人群中虚妄的孤独。</span></span>', '2015-09-17 14:33:18', '2015-09-17 14:40:54', '1', '', '1', '0', '1', '8', 'resource/content/2015/09/17/201509171433184.jpg', '1', '1', null, '4', '0', '0', 'pages/c/2015/09/17/67PDNCFUeZ.html', '', '', '', '2', '7', null, null, null, null, '318', '318', '201509171433184_small.jpg');
INSERT INTO `keke_content` VALUES ('68', 'Spring初识', '<strong style=\"line-height: 22.3999996185303px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\">keke老师寄语：&nbsp;</span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-size:20px;\">这个是一个全新的开始，潭州学院所以的VIP学员，路程已经出发必须坚持到最后。<br />\n<br />\n1:认识Spring</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n创始人：Rod Johson。<br />\n<br />\n特点：<br />\n<br />\na：方便解耦，简化开发，提升性能(IOC)<br />\n&nbsp; IOC它是Spring核心业务模块，它是将类和类之间的依赖从代码中脱离出来。IOC容器 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;(BeanFactory(ApplicationContext,FileSytemApplcationContext,WebApplicationContext))<br />\n&nbsp; 这个容器负责类和类之间对象创建，拼接，管理(存储)，获取。&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\nb：Aop面向切面的编程<br />\nc：声明式事务支持<br />\nd：方便程序的调试<br />\ne: 方便集成各大优秀的框架<br />\nf: &nbsp;Java源代码学习的典范<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size:20px;\">2:Spring的体系结构</span></strong>\n\n<div class=\"tzui-img\"><img src=\"http://keke.tanzhouedu.com/resource/content/2015/10/08/201510082130074.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" /></div>\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size:20px;\">2:Java的面向对象，封装，继承，多态。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nJava的本质是什么：面向对象<br />\n对象是怎么创建的: new<br />\n对象职责是：调用方法和属性(给属性赋值，调用方法，使用)<br />\n<br />\n3JavaBean的作用<br />\na: 为什么要生成getter/setter呢? (<span style=\"font-size:20px;\"><strong>就是为了给属性赋值</strong></span>)<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp;就是因为私有属性无法赋值，<br />\n<br />\nb:extends的作用是什么. 达到属性共享方法共用的目的<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size:20px;\">3:快速搭建一个SpringMVC框架</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n技术体系：Springmvc+SpringJdbcTemplate +Mysql+Jsp<br />\n版本：Jdk1.7+Tomcat7.0+Spring4.15<br />\n工具：myeclipse2014<br />\n数据库工具：navicat11.x<br />\n功能点：实现用户的添加和查询<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><strong>第一步：下载Spring的安装压缩包</strong></span><br />\n<br />\nhttp://maven.springframework.org/release/org/springframework/spring/<br />\n项目所需要的包结构如下：<br />\ncommons-collections-3.1.jar<br />\ncommons-dbcp-1.2.1.jar<br />\ncommons-lang3-3.1.jar<br />\ncommons-logging-1.1.3.jar<br />\ncommons-pool-1.2.jar<br />\nmysql-connector-java-5.1.6-bin.jar<br />\nspring-aop-4.1.5.RELEASE.jar<br />\nspring-beans-4.1.5.RELEASE.jar<br />\nspring-context-4.1.5.RELEASE.jar<br />\nspring-context-support-4.1.5.RELEASE.jar<br />\nspring-core-4.1.5.RELEASE.jar<br />\nspring-expression-4.1.5.RELEASE.jar<br />\nspring-jdbc-4.1.5.RELEASE.jar<br />\nspring-orm-4.1.5.RELEASE.jar<br />\nspring-test-4.1.5.RELEASE.jar<br />\nspring-tx-4.1.5.RELEASE.jar<br />\nspring-web-4.1.5.RELEASE.jar<br />\nspring-webmvc-4.1.5.RELEASE.jar<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">第二步：新建一个数据tzspring和表tz_user</span></strong><br />\n&nbsp;\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"line-height:20px; font-size:14px;font-family:Consolas,Courier New,Inconsolata-g,DejaVu Sans Mono,微软雅黑,宋体;color:#f9f9f9;\" width=\"100%\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr style=\"background-color:#1b2426;\" valign=\"top\">\n			<td style=\"border:0px; border-right-color:#435a5f; border-right-width:3px; color:#b9bdb6; border-right-style:solid; text-align:right; padding-right:5px; width:40px;\">1</td>\n			<td style=\"border:0px; padding-left:10px; text-align:left;\">脚本命令：</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr style=\"background-color:#323232;\" valign=\"top\">\n			<td style=\"border:0px; border-right-color:#435a5f; border-right-width:3px; color:#b9bdb6; border-right-style:solid; text-align:right; padding-right:5px; width:40px;\">2</td>\n			<td style=\"border:0px; padding-left:10px; text-align:left;\">&nbsp;</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr style=\"background-color:#1b2426;\" valign=\"top\">\n			<td style=\"border:0px; border-right-color:#435a5f; border-right-width:3px; color:#b9bdb6; border-right-style:solid; text-align:right; padding-right:5px; width:40px;\">3</td>\n			<td style=\"border:0px; padding-left:10px; text-align:left;\">CREATE&nbsp;TABLE&nbsp;`tz_user`&nbsp;(</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr style=\"background-color:#323232;\" valign=\"top\">\n			<td style=\"border:0px; border-right-color:#435a5f; border-right-width:3px; color:#b9bdb6; border-right-style:solid; text-align:right; padding-right:5px; width:40px;\">4</td>\n			<td style=\"border:0px; padding-left:10px; text-align:left;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;`id`&nbsp;int(11)&nbsp;NOT&nbsp;NULL&nbsp;AUTO_INCREMENT,</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr style=\"background-color:#1b2426;\" valign=\"top\">\n			<td style=\"border:0px; border-right-color:#435a5f; border-right-width:3px; color:#b9bdb6; border-right-style:solid; text-align:right; padding-right:5px; width:40px;\">5</td>\n			<td style=\"border:0px; padding-left:10px; text-align:left;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;`username`&nbsp;varchar(100)&nbsp;DEFAULT&nbsp;NULL,</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr style=\"background-color:#323232;\" valign=\"top\">\n			<td style=\"border:0px; border-right-color:#435a5f; border-right-width:3px; color:#b9bdb6; border-right-style:solid; text-align:right; padding-right:5px; width:40px;\">6</td>\n			<td style=\"border:0px; padding-left:10px; text-align:left;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;`password`&nbsp;varchar(100)&nbsp;DEFAULT&nbsp;NULL,</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr style=\"background-color:#1b2426;\" valign=\"top\">\n			<td style=\"border:0px; border-right-color:#435a5f; border-right-width:3px; color:#b9bdb6; border-right-style:solid; text-align:right; padding-right:5px; width:40px;\">7</td>\n			<td style=\"border:0px; padding-left:10px; text-align:left;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;`age`&nbsp;int(11)&nbsp;DEFAULT&nbsp;NULL,</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr style=\"background-color:#323232;\" valign=\"top\">\n			<td style=\"border:0px; border-right-color:#435a5f; border-right-width:3px; color:#b9bdb6; border-right-style:solid; text-align:right; padding-right:5px; width:40px;\">8</td>\n			<td style=\"border:0px; padding-left:10px; text-align:left;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;`address`&nbsp;varchar(255)&nbsp;DEFAULT&nbsp;NULL,</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr style=\"background-color:#1b2426;\" valign=\"top\">\n			<td style=\"border:0px; border-right-color:#435a5f; border-right-width:3px; color:#b9bdb6; border-right-style:solid; text-align:right; padding-right:5px; width:40px;\">9</td>\n			<td style=\"border:0px; padding-left:10px; text-align:left;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;`email`&nbsp;varchar(100)&nbsp;DEFAULT&nbsp;NULL,</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr style=\"background-color:#323232;\" valign=\"top\">\n			<td style=\"border:0px; border-right-color:#435a5f; border-right-width:3px; color:#b9bdb6; border-right-style:solid; text-align:right; padding-right:5px; width:40px;\">10</td>\n			<td style=\"border:0px; padding-left:10px; text-align:left;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;`create_time`&nbsp;timestamp&nbsp;NOT&nbsp;NULL&nbsp;DEFAULT&nbsp;CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr style=\"background-color:#1b2426;\" valign=\"top\">\n			<td style=\"border:0px; border-right-color:#435a5f; border-right-width:3px; color:#b9bdb6; border-right-style:solid; text-align:right; padding-right:5px; width:40px;\">11</td>\n			<td style=\"border:0px; padding-left:10px; text-align:left;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;PRIMARY&nbsp;KEY&nbsp;(`id`)</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr style=\"background-color:#323232;\" valign=\"top\">\n			<td style=\"border:0px; border-right-color:#435a5f; border-right-width:3px; color:#b9bdb6; border-right-style:solid; text-align:right; padding-right:5px; width:40px;\">12</td>\n			<td style=\"border:0px; padding-left:10px; text-align:left;\">)&nbsp;ENGINE=InnoDB&nbsp;AUTO_INCREMENT=8&nbsp;DEFAULT&nbsp;CHARSET=utf8</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">第三步：新建一个项目tzspringmvc的javaweb工程结构目录如下</span></strong><br />\n&nbsp;\n<div class=\"tzui-img\">\n<div class=\"tzui-img\"><img src=\"http://keke.tanzhouedu.com/resource/content/2015/10/09/201510091422101.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" /></div>\n</div>\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">第四步：在applicationContext.xml添加如下代码，扫包操作:</span></strong>\n\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"line-height:20px; font-size:14px;font-family:Consolas,Courier New,Inconsolata-g,DejaVu Sans Mono,微软雅黑,宋体;color:#f9f9f9;\" width=\"100%\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr style=\"ba